% break-on-error.trx -- engine-level break-on-error gate (no UI).
% A recorder callback stands in for the inspector: the /error event must
% fire for the uncaught name below, and after the callback returns the
% error must complete with its normal diagnostic and /undefined exit
% code (40).  run_cli_tests.sh pins both.
{ /e exch def (halt-tag=) print e tag-name = debug-continue } debug-on-event
true debug-break-on-error
(armed) =
no-such-op-zzz
